t%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaria%20Campos%2C%20the%20director%20of%20client%20services%20at%20Las%20Rosadas%2C%20a%20collection%20of%20private%20villas%20and%20residences%20along%20Costalegre%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Chamela%2C%20where%20she%20said%20the%20coast%20was%20typically%20called%20Costa%20Sur.%20In%201990%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Jalisco%20officially%20deemed%20the%20region%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0016328714002067%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epriority%20tourism%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20named%20it%20the%20Costalegre%20Ecological%20Tourism%20Corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-stressful-job-moved-to-finland-with-best-friend-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFinland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20data%20to%20support%20its%20designation%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-finland-is-the-happiest-country-former-international-student-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehappiest%20country%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Costalegre%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%26quot%3Bcoast%20of%20joy%2C%26quot%3B%20taunts%20its%20title%20casually%20and%20confidently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20guests%20wind%20up%20in%20the%20region%2C%20I%20was%20rarely%20told%20it%20was%20because%20they%20wanted%20to%20visit%20Costalegre.%20Some%20people%20stumbled%20on%20a%20property%20while%20researching%20Puerto%20Vallarta%3B%20most%20received%20a%20rave%20review%20from%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikely%2C%20if%20you've%20heard%20of%20Costalegre%2C%20it's%20because%20of%20the%20private%20community%20of%20Careyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223872%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gian%20Franco%20Brignone%20at%20Careyes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682760103fe8d392836613fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223098%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGian%20Franco%20Brignone%20at%20Careyes.%3Cp%3ECareyes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201968%2C%20Italian%20banker%20Gian%20Franco%20Brignone%20flew%20over%20Mexico's%20Pacific%20Coast.%20Impressed%20by%20what%20he%20saw%20from%20the%20small%20Cessna%20plane%2C%20he%20purchased%2013%2C000%20acres%20of%20the%20coastline%20to%20build%20a%20colorful%20retreat.%20(Careyes%20declined%20to%20share%20how%20much%20Brignone%20paid%20for%20the%20land.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20not%20anything%20when%20my%20father%20first%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20Emanuela%20Brignone%20Cattaneo%2C%20Brignone's%20daughter%2C%20told%20me%20over%20dinner%20one%20evening.%20%26quot%3BMy%20father%20would%20show%20friends%2C%20and%20then%20those%20friends%20would%20buy%20land.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECareyes%20now%20sits%20on%2035%2C000%20acres%20with%20a%2025%2C000-acre%20biosphere%2C%2046%20multimillion-dollar%20villas%2C%2040%20casitas%2C%2055%20suites%2C%20and%20three%20bungalows.%20It's%20a%20colorful%20neighborhood%20with%20villas%20in%20cobalt%20blues%2C%20highlighter%20yellows%2C%20and%20dusty%20pinks.%20A%20few%20dozen%20permanent%20residents%20call%20it%20home%2C%20but%20most%20properties%20cater%20to%20vacationers%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20Mediterranean%20meets%20Mexico%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20Kessler%2C%20a%20Careyes%20resident%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20KIPR%20Global%2C%20the%20public%20relations%20agency%20that%20represents%20Careyes%2C%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20villa%20in%20Careyes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f6949c6ad288d1481aef8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20villa%20in%20Careyes.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Careyes'%20architecture%20and%20color%20palette%20leave%20an%20im