22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETulum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Once%20you%20arrive%20at%20a%20resort%2C%20you%20won't%20see%20other%20buildings%20stretching%20into%20the%20sky.%20There%20are%20no%20middle-tier%20resorts%20with%20crowded%20pools%20or%20clubs%20bumping%20the%20bass%20late%20into%20the%20night.%20Souvenir%20shops%20are%20limited%20to%20small%20resort%20boutiques%20with%20local%20art%20instead%20of%20shot%20glasses%20and%20T-shirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20at%20Las%20Rosadas%20on%20Costalegre.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f6edd6ffb6822ec61433a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20at%20Las%20Rosadas%20on%20Costalegre.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Costalegre%20is%20quiet%20and%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20times%20throughout%20my%20trip%2C%20it%20was%20just%20me%20and%20my%20travel%20partner%20on%20a%20beach%20in%20complete%20solitude%2C%20something%20that%20feels%20impossible%20to%20discover%20in%20today's%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20seclusion%20is%20exactly%20what%20appeals%20to%20the%20residents%20and%20vacationers%20enamored%20by%20the%20Happy%20Coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20there%20are%20too%20many%20places%20in%20the%20world%20where%20you%20can%20walk%20three%20kilometers%20down%20the%20coast%20and%20there's%20no%20one%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Viviana%20Dean%2C%20who%20lives%20full-time%20in%20Careyes%2C%20told%20me%20while%20sipping%20a%20margarita%20overlooking%20the%20ocean.%20%26quot%3BEven%20after%2030%20years%2C%20I%20can't%20believe%20I'm%20alone%20in%20this%20beautiful%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20plenty%20love%20Costalegre%2C%20Kessler%20said%20that's%20not%20the%20case%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20people%20that%20want%20Chanel%20and%20Gucci%20and%20all%20