www.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmark-carneys-daughter-and-belgian-princess-entangled-in-harvard-trump-row-8495348%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20high-profile%20student%20caught%20between%20the%20crosshairs%20is%20Princess%20Elisabeth%20of%20Belgium.%20She%20is%20the%20heir%20to%20the%20Belgian%20throne%20and%20has%20just%20completed%20her%20first%20year%20in%20a%20two-year%20masters%20program%20in%20public%20policy%20at%20the%20Harvard%20Kennedy%20School.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20is%20using%20helium-filled%20balloons%20to%20extend%20the%20range%20of%20its%20attack%20drones%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerobavovna%20develops%20tethered%20aerostat%20systems%20equipped%20with%20specialized%20equipment.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68249c4f68a29290080143a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAerobavovna%20develops%20aerostat%20systems%20with%20specialized%20equipment.%3Cp%3EAerobavovna%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAerobavovna%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20startup%2C%20is%20making%20helium-filled%20balloons%20to%20aid%20Ukraine's%20drone%20attacks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20balloons%20help%20to%20keep%20drones%20on%20the%20grid%20when%20they're%20on%20the%20ground%20or%20flying%20low.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAerobavovna's%20CEO%20told%20BI%20that%2050%20aerostats%20are%20deployed%20along%20the%20frontline.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAgainst%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Ukraine's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-lots-drone-types-give-advantages-but-also-downsides-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrone-packed%20skies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20startup%20is%20offering%20a%20surprisingly%20low-tech%20solution%20to%20a%20modern%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAerobavovna%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20in%202023%2C%20is%20supplying%20Ukraine's%20military%20with%20tethered%2C%20helium-filled%20balloons%20equipped%20with%20airborne%20radio%20repeaters%2C%20extending%20the%20range%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20country's%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20has%20been%20defined%20by%20drone%20warfare%2C%20but%20drone%20operators%20have%20faced%20a%20number%20of%20challenges%2C%20including%20line-of-sight%20obstacles%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20drones%20to%20lose%20contact%20if%20radio%20signals%20are%20disrupted%2C%20and%20electronic%20warfare%20systems%2C%20which%20can%20jam%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20Aerobavovna%20comes%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20aerostats%20are%20designed%20for%20surveillance%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20first-person-view%20(FPV)%20drone%20signal%20transmission%2C%20and%20help%20establish%20stable%20communication%20signals%20in%20the%20battlefield's%20tricky%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFitted%20with%20antennas%20and%20radio%20repeaters%2C%20Aerobavovna's%20aerostats%20anchor%20high%20over%20the%20battlefield%20to%20help%20Ukrainian%20drones%20continue%20operating%20in%20spite%20of%20obstacles%20and%20to%20maintain%20comms%20over%20much%20greater%20distances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20%26quot%3Bsome%20kind%20of%20airborne%20radio%20repeater%20that%20allows%20drones%20to%20fly%20closer%20to%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20Yuriy%20Vysoven%2C%20Aerobavovna's%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20ground%20drones%2C%20it's%20crucial%20because%20their%20ground-to-ground%20signal%20would%20only%20reach%20the%20first%20hill%3B%20beyond%20that%2C%20you%20lose%20direct%20line%20of%20sight%20and%2C%20consequently%2C%20the%20connection%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20about%2050%20balloons%20were%20deployed%20%26quot%3Ball%20around%20the%20front%20line%26quot%3B%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20aerostats%20aren't%20new%20technology%2C%20Aerobavovna's%20products%20have%20been%20designed%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20modern%20battlefield%2C%20allowing%20for%20rapid%20deployment%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAerobavovna's%20balloons%2C%20which%20the%20firm%20says%20can%20be%20deployed%20in%20five%20to%2025%20minutes%2C%20are%20made%20with%20lightweight%20polymers%20and%20can%20remain%20airborne%20for%20up%20to%20seven%20days.%20They%20can%20lift%20repeater%20systems%20up%20to%20a%20height%20of%201%20km%20(about%200.6%20miles)%20and%20carry%20a%20payload%20of%20up%20to%2025%20kg%20(around%2055%20lbs)%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20which%C2%A0says%20it%20produces%20around%2010%20to%2020%20balloons%20per%20month%2C%C2%A0recently%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20developed%20a%20new%20aerostat%20capable%20of%20carrying%20more%20advanced%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilitarnyi.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2Faerobavovna-develops-aerostat-capable-of-lifting-30-kg-payloads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMilitarnyi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20engineers%20from%20Aerobavovna%20said%20they%20had%20created%20a%20new%20model%20that%20can%20hold%20a%20payload%20of%20up%20to%2066%20lbs%2C%20enabling%20it%20to%20carry%20more%20powerful%20equipment%20such%20as%20electronic%20warfare%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20company%20has%20found%20success%20supplying%20tethered%20aerostats%20to%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20grapple%20with%20technical%20and%20structural%20hurdles%20as%20it%20scales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20persistent%20challenge%20is%20maintaining%20stability%20and%20precision%20in%20airborne%20conditions%2C%20especially%20critical%20for%20payloads%20like%20FPV%20drone%20radio%20repeaters%2C%20which%20require%20highly%20accurate%20antenna%20positioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStability%20is%20a%20big%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Vysoven%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20FPV%20drone%20radio%20repeaters%2C%20you%20need%20to%20position%20the%20antennas%20really%2C%20really%20precisely%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20wind%20and%20turbulence%20make%20that%20very%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunding%20also%20remains%20a%20major%20constraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20strong%20demand%20and%20a%20battlefield-proven%20product%2C%20capital%20is%20scarce%20for%20Ukrainian%20hardware%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVysoven%20said%20the%20company%20has%20received%20investment%20offers%20in%20the%20range%20of%20%2440%20million%2C%20but%20considers%20that%20far%20below%20what's%20needed%20and%20called%20that%20figure%20%26quot%3Ba%20shame.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20California%2C%20you%20can%20raise%20that%20with%20just%20a%20pitch%20deck%20and%20a%20latte.%20I%20have%20a%20real%20product%2C%2030%20engineers%20building%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20already%20deployed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20still%20struggle%20to%20raise%20enough%20to%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-helium-balloons-extend-range-attack-drones-russia-aerobavovna-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748073602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68249c6a3fe8d3928365cbb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-helium-balloons-extend-range-attack-drones-russia-aerobavovna-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20startup%20Aerobavovna%20is%20making%20waves%20with%20a%20low-tech%20warfare%20solution%3A%20helium-filled%20aerostats%20balloons%20that%20extend%20drone%20communications.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-helium-balloons-extend-rang