he%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20to%20other%20women%20experiencing%20the%20same%20feeling%20of%20empowerment%20from%20running%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20age%20or%20ability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20race%2C%20Switzer%2C%20at%20the%20time%20a%2020-year-old%20journalism%20student%20at%20Syracuse%20University%2C%20trained%20with%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-student-athlete-tiktok-influencer-balances-school-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollege's%20cross-country%3C%2Fa%3E%20team%20for%20a%20year%20(it%20was%20against%20collegiate%20rules%20for%20a%20woman%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20sport).%20She%20couldn't%20keep%20up%20with%20most%20of%20the%20men%20on%20the%20team%2C%20so%20the%20assistant%20coach%2C%20Arnie%20Briggs%2C%20began%20training%20with%20her%20separately%20as%20he%20recovered%20from%20a%20knee%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20better%20and%20stronger%2C%26quot%3B%20Switzer%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20got%20up%20to%20five%20miles%20and%20then%20seven%20and%20then%2011.%20The%20guys%20on%20the%20cross%20country%20team%20wouldn't%20come%20out%20with%20us%20after%2020%20kilometers%2C%20but%20that's%20when%20I%20could%20keep%20up%20with%20them%20because%20they%20didn't%20have%20the%20endurance%20I%20had.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20runs%2C%20Switzer%20and%20Briggs%20discussed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-ran-my-first-marathon-advice-mistakes-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarathons%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Briggs%20had%20run%20the%20Boston%20Marathon%2015%20times%20but%20didn't%20believe%20that%20a%20woman%20could%20run%20that%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20then%20he%20said%2C%20'Look%2C%20if%20any%20woman%20could%2C%20I%20would%20believe%20it%20was%20you.%20But%20you%20would%20have%20to%20prove%20it%20to%20me%2C%20and%20then%20I'd%20take%20you%20to%20Boston.'%20I%20said%2C%20'Hot