idential%20debates%2C%20her%20longtime%20partners%20Bill%20Isaacson%20and%20Jessica%20Phillips%2C%20and%20the%20former%20prosecutor%20Jeannie%20Rhee%20said%20in%20an%20email%20addressed%20to%20%26quot%3Bpartners%20and%20friends%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20are%20starting%20their%20own%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high-profile%20departures%20underscore%20the%20ongoing%20turmoil%20at%20Big%20Law%20firms%20surrounding%20the%20firms'%20handling%20of%20punitive%20executive%20actions%20from%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration.%20The%20departing%20lawyers%20did%20not%20give%20a%20reason%20for%20leaving%20in%20their%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20major%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-blocks-donald-trump-executive-order-big-law-perkins-coie-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerkins%20Coie%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-executive-order-targeting-jenner-block-big-law-unconstitutional-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJenner%20%26amp%3B%20Block%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20chose%20to%20challenge%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20orders%20in%20court%2C%20and%20have%20so%20far%20been%20successful%20after%20two%20judges%20declared%20two%20different%20orders%20unconstitutional.%20Other%20firms%2C%20including%20Paul%20Weiss%2C%20chose%20to%20make%20deals%20with%20the%20administration%2C%20prompting%20concern%20among%20associates%20and%20partners%20over%20their%20willingness%20to%20cooperate%20rather%20than%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20firm's%20name%20isn't%20clear.%20Since%20April%2C%20several%20domain%20names%20containing%20Dunn's%20name%20and%20those%20of%20other%20lawyers%20have%20been%20registered%20anonymously.%20None%20of%20the%20websites%20contains%20any%20details%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20clear%20who%20registered%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyers%20have%20represented%20prominent%20clients%20like%20Google%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Apple%20over%20the%20years.%20Isaacson%20is%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20top%20antitrust%20litigators.%20Antitrust%20issues%20have%20been%20a%20focus%20for%20both%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Trump%2C%20who%20have%20criticized%20the%20power%20of%20large%20tech%20companies.%20Rhee%20managed%20the%20firm's%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20office%2C%20and%20Dunn%20co-chaired%20its%20litigation%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20an%20honor%20to%20work%20alongside%20such%20talented%20lawyers%20and%20to%20call%20so%20many%20of%20you%20our%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20departing%20email%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20to%20continue%20to%20collaborate%20with%20all%20of%20you%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come%20and%20are%20incredibly%20grateful%20for%20your%20warm%20and%20generous%20partnership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Weiss's%20chair%2C%20Brad%20Karp%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20grateful%20to%20Bill%2C%20Jeannie%2C%20Jessica%2C%20and%20Karen%20for%20their%20many%20contributions%20to%20the%20firm.%20We%20wish%20them%20well%20in%20their%20future%20endeavors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20departures%20come%20several%20months%20after%20the%20Trump%20administration%20began%20targeting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-memo-orders-big-law-firms-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Law%3C%2Fa%3E%20firms%20with%20punitive%20executive%20actions.%20Among%20them%20was%20Paul%20Weiss%2C%20which%20faced%20an%20executive%20order%20that%20revoked%20the%20security%20clearances%20of%20the%20firm's%20attorneys%20and%20ordered%20a%20review%20of%20its%20government%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2020%2C%20Trump%20announced%20on%20Truth%20Social%20that%20he%20would%20drop%20the%20executive%20order%20against%20Paul%20Weiss%20after%20negotiating%20a%20deal%20that%20would%20require%20the%20firm%20to%20end%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F