dio%20out%2C%20RS-232C%2C%20RF%20antenna%2C%20and%20an%20IR%20blaster%20port.%20The%20TV%20also%20supports%20Bluetooth%205.3%20and%20WiFi%206E%20connectivity.%20The%20power%20cable%20is%20hard-wired%20and%20extends%20from%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20set.%20The%20back%20of%20the%20panel%20has%20an%20interesting%20textured%20marble%20look%20and%20feel.%20I'll%20admit%20that%20I%20dig%20it%2C%20but%20am%20also%20a%20bit%20surprised%20when%20cool%20design%20elements%20like%20this%20are%20so%20hidden%2C%20considering%20few%20are%20likely%20to%20see%20the%20panel's%20rear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20C5's%20biggest%20changes%20isn't%20even%20on%20the%20TV%20itself.%20It's%20a%20new%20design%20for%20LG's%20Magic%20Remote.%20I've%20never%20been%20much%20of%20a%20Magic%20Remote%20fan%2C%20so%20I%20was%20excited%20that%20a%20change%20was%20in%20store.%20While%20the%20old%20Magic%20Remote%20had%20a%20chunky%20curved%20design%20that%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20ergonomic%20(I%20never%20found%20it%20to%20be)%2C%20the%20new%20one%20has%20a%20more%20traditional%20rectangular%20design.%20It%20fits%20more%20comfortably%20in%20my%20hand%2C%20and%20there%20are%20significantly%20fewer%20buttons%2C%20as%20the%20redesign%20has%20removed%20all%20number%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person's%20hand%20holding%20an%20LG%20TV%20remote%20in%20front%20of%20a%20C5%20OLED.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68308f546ffb6822ec6158ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20remote's%20new%20design%20is%20more%20comfortable%20and%20streamlined%2C%20but%20it's%20now%20missing%20dedicated%20mute%20and%20input%20buttons.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Higgins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20vast%20improvement%20over%20previous%20iterations%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20not%20perfect.%20For%20one%2C%20it%20isn't%20backlit%2C%20which%20is%20annoying%20in%20a%20dark%20room%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20input%20select%20button.%20Instead%2C%20you%20need%20to%20navigate%20through%20the%20Home%20menu%20to%20select%20an%20input%20on%20screen.%20There%20also%20isn't%20a%20dedicated%20mute%20button.%20Muting%20can%20still%20be%20achieved%20by%20holding%20the%20volume%20down%20button.%20But%20by%20mapping%20the%20function%20this%20way%2C%20it's%20now%20difficult%20to%20quickly%20lower%20the%20volume%20rather%20than%20completely%20mute%20it.%20It's%20just%20an%20odd%20design%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Magic%20Remote%20still%20has%20its%20motion%20control%20tech%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20wave%20it%20around%20like%20a%20wand%20to%20move%20a%20virtual%20cursor%20on%20the%20screen.%20This%20remains%20a%20divisive%20feature%2C%20and%20there's%20still%20no%20way%20to%20turn%20it%20off%20completely.%20You%20have%20the%20option%20to%20click%20down%20on%20a%20directional%20pad%20to%20navigate%20the%20TV%20in%20a%20traditional%20manner%2C%20but%20the%20motion%20controls%20get%20reactivated%20if%20you%20move%20the%20scroll%20wheel.%20Hopefully%2C%20at%20some%20point%20in%20the%20future%2C%20LG%20will%20add%20a%20way%20to%20fully%20deactivate%20the%20wand%20and%20just%20allow%20it%20to%20be%20a%20regular%20remote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22781cee11-d279-4517-ad4a-78b95b3fca55%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20quality%5C%22%3EThe%20C5%20delivers%20great%20picture%20quality%20with%20a%20touch%20more%20brightness%20than%20the%20C4%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20C5%20OLED%20on%20a%20media%20console%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20geyser.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68309b22c6ad288d1481c84a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELG's%20C5%20offers%20impressive%20image%20quality%20for%20a%20midrange%20OLED.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Higgins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETVs%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20those%20in%20the%20midrange%20class%20and%20above%20%E2%80%94%20have%20grown%20so%20close%20in%20performance%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20find%20significant%20fault%20with%20all%20that%20much.%20This%20is%20even%20more%20true%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-oled-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20OLED%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20no%20matter%20the%20price%20point%2C%20they%20have%20perfect%20black%20levels%20at%20the%20pixel%20level%20(since%20the%20pixels%20can%20actually%20turn%20off)%20and%20they're%20generally%20highly%20color%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20LG%20C5%20is%20no%20exception.%20I%20measured%20the%20C5%20using%20a%20Portrait%20Displays%20C6%20HDR5000%20colorimeter%2C%20G1%20pattern%20generator%2C%20Konica%20Minolta%20LS-100%20light%20meter%2C%20and%20Calman%20calibration%20software.%20The%20LG%20C5%20ships%20in%20Auto%20Power%20Save%20mode%2C%20which%20has%20an%20extreme%20blue%20tint%20and%20overbrightens%20most%20of%20the%20midtone%20grays.%20For%20an%20accurate%20picture%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20you%20should%20do%20is%20switch%20into%20either%20Filmmaker%20or%20Cinema%20mode.%20After%20that%2C%20navigate%20to%20the%20energy%20saving%20option%20in%20the%20General%20settings%20menu%20and%20change%20Energy%20Saving%20Step%20from%20Auto%20to%20Off.%20This%20will%20unlock%20the%20brightness%20adjustments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Filmmaker%20and%20Cinema%20modes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh%20dynamic%20range%3C%2Fa%3E%20(HDR)%20grayscale%20accuracy%20tracks%20incredibly%20well.%20DeltaE%20(dE)%20errors%2C%20which%20indicate%20how%20close%20the%20measurements%20are%20to%20perfect%20readings%20(the%20lower%20the%20better)%2C%20were%20under%20the%20perceptible%20value%20of%202.3.%20The%20C5%20covers%2098.6%25%20of%20the%20P3%20color%20gamut%20and%2073.34%25%20of%20BT.2020%2C%20both%20improvements%20over%20last%20year's%20C4.%20Standard%20dynamic%20range%20(SDR)%20performance%20is%20equally%20impressive%2C%20with%20an%20average%20grayscale%20dE%20of%20just%201.9%2C%20a%20gamma%20of%202.21%2C%20and%2098.7%25%20coverage%20of%20Rec.709%20(the%20standard%20SDR%20color%20gamut%20used%20for%20most%20cable%2C%20satellite%2C%20and%20live%20TV%20streaming%20services).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20SDR%20with%20brightness%20set%20to%20100%2C%20the%20C5%20puts%20out%20410%20nits%20in%20a%2010%25%20window.%20If%20you%20plan%20on%20watching%20SDR%20content%20in%20a%20suitably%20dark%20room%2C%20a%20brightness%20setting%20of%2011%20brings%20light%20output%20down%20to%20104%20nits%2C%20just%20above%20the%20target%20of%20100.%20If%20you%20prefer%20a%20slightly%20brighter%20picture%20for%20your%20SDR%20content%2C%20a%20setting%20of%2040%20brings%20light%20output%20up%20to%20202%20nits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20HDR%20signal%2C%20the%20LG%20C5%20is%20capable%20of%20a%20bit%20more%20brightness%20than%20last%20year's%20C4.%20Where%20the%20C4%20measured%20just%20under%201%2C000%20nits%20with%20a%2010%25%20window%2C%20the%20C5%20hit%201%2C174%20nits.%20The%20200%20nit%20improvement%20is%20enough%20to%20see%20a%20difference%2C%20and%20HDR%20content%20pops%20a%20bit%20more.%20But%20it%20still%20isn't%20competing%20with%20the%20C5's%20big%20brother%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109693116kt-20%26h%3Db69cd1d7dd719a4980b67de475485d4c865725af23222a7e2fbba47e53e8f8c2%26postID%3D68306d1779dac8da3aaf88db%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Flg-c5-oled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0DYQR8R98%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EG5%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20hit%20over%202%2C000%20nits%2C%20or%20flagship%20Mini%20LED%20TVs%20from%20Hisense%20and%20TCL%20that%20can%20surpass%20a%20whopping%204%2C000%20nits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20C5%20OLED%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20beaver.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68309c306ffb6822ec615bd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHDR%20content%20looks%20great%20thanks%20to%20the%20C5's%20high-contrast%20OLED%20panel.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Higgins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20this%20brightness%20mean%20with%20actual%20content%2C%20though%3F%20Small%2C%20bright%20portions%20of%20the%20screen%20(called%20specular%20highlights)%20sparkle%20and%20add%20life%20to%20the%20picture%20when%20watching%20HDR%20movies%20and%20shows.%20This%20is%20especially%20true%20because%20of%20OLED%20tech's%20ability%20to%20light%20a%20single%20pixel%20at%20a%20time.%20I%20was%20lucky%20to%20have%20my%20review%20period%20line%20up%20with%20the%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandor-season-two-review-star-wars-masterpiece-cast-timeless-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAndor%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20season%20two%2C%20and%20just%20the%20opening%20title%20sequence%2C%20where%20the%20word%20Andor%20appears%20amid%20a%20space%20sky%20littered%20with%20stars%2C%20looked%20stunning.%20The%20blaster%20fire%20from%20the%20stolen%20TIE%20prototype%20lit%20up%20the%20Yavin%20IV%20night%2C%20as%20did%20the%20resulting%20explosions%20against%20the%20dark%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDark%20shadows%20also%20provide%20great%20detail.%20The%20piano%20against%20the%20back%20wall%20of%20Sapper%20Morton's%20home%20in%20the%20early%20scenes%20of%20%26quot%3BBlade%20Runner%202049%26quot%3B%20stands%20apart%20and%20gives%20the%20image%20great%20dimensionality.%20On%20less%20capable%20TVs%2C%20the%20piano%20in%20this%20sequence%20tends%20to%20meld%20into%20the%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColors%20on%20the%20C5%20looked%20lush%20and%20rich.%20The%20hills%20of%20the%20Shire%20and%20the%20forests%20around%20Rivendell%20in%20%26quot%3BFellowship%20of%20the%20Ring%26quot%3B%20were%20inviting%20and%20realistic.%20And%20the%20fireworks%20at%20Bilbo's%20birthday%20celebration%20sparkled%20with%20light%20and%20color%20to%20the%20delight%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20some%20reports%20of%20display-related%20posterization%2Ffalse%20contouring%20(blocky%20rather%20than%20smooth%20gradations%20of%20colors%20and%20shadows)%20when%20watching%20certain%20HDR10%20videos%20on%20the%20C5.%20However%2C%20this%20didn't%20occur%20during%20my%20testing%2C%20even%20when%20watching%20several%20dark%2Fnear-dark%20scenes%20in%20%26quot%3BBlade%20Runner%202049%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDeathly%20Hallows%20Part%202%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20be%20tricky%20for%20some%20TVs%20to%20handle.%20It's%20possible%20the%20C5%20may%20display%20some%20contouring%20in%20isolated%20instances%2C%20but%20this%20appears%20to%20be%20tied%20to%20specific%20conditions%20rather%20than%20being%20a%20widespread%20flaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20C4%20and%20past%20C-Series%20models%2C%20the%20C5%20uses%20a%20traditional%20WOLED%20panel%20rather%20than%20a%20Quantum%20Dot%20OLED%20(QD-OLED)%20panel%2C%20which%20is%20used%20on%20some%20competing%20Samsung%20TVs%2C%20like%20the%20comparatively%20priced%20S90%20series.%20The%20main%20shortcomings%20of%20WOLED%20when%20compared%20to%20QD-OLED%20are%20color%20volume%20and%20brightness.%20As%20such%2C%20I%20expect%20Samsung's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109693116kt-20%26h%3D7897de744beb5112e000b65614f9aeb21954b282786105ca9f81767b002ff9ec%26postID%3D68306d1779dac8da3aaf88db%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Flg-c5-oled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0DXMJGQWC%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES90F%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20brighter%20and%20have%20slightly%20wider%20color%20capabilities%20than%20the%20C5.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20marginal%20difference%20in%20color%20gamut%20won't%20make%20much%20of%20an%20impact%2C%20but%20the%20jump%20in%20brightness%20should%20allow%20the%20S90F%20to%20deliver%20more%20sparkling%20highlights%20in%20certain%20HDR%20content.%20I'll%20be%20testing%20the%20S90F%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20so%20check%20back%20for%20details%20on%20how%20it%20compares%20to%20the%20C5.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e17e8f7d-8689-4bd9-b225-d06055a97d7b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Gaming%20performance%5C%22%3EThe%20LG%20C5%20is%20a%20very%20capable%20gaming%20TV%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20Game%20Optimizer%20menu%20on%20an%20LG%20C5%20OLED%20TV%20while%20playing%20a%20game%20on%20a%20PS5.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68309ab8c6ad288d1481c832%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20C5%20has%20a%20handy%20Game%20Optimizer%20menu%2C%20and%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20first%20LG%20TVs%20to%20support%20the%20Xbox%20app.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Higgins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20I've%20recommended%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109693116kt-20%26h%3Df345fe01195470e00dd2d1c3fca548c2ccf62c8056e1550218b2498caa0155ec%26postID%3D68306d1779dac8da3aaf88db%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Flg-c5-oled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSAMSUNG-Tracking-Xcelerator-Enhancer-Upscaling%252Fdp%252FB0CV9VGMPT%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamsung%20S90D%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20friends%20and%20readers%20as%20a%20gaming-centric%20television.%20It%20set%20itself%20apart%20from%20many%20direct%20competitors%20by%20supporting%20cloud%20gaming%20through%20the%20Xbox%20app%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fxbox-game-pass%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGame%20Pass%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allowing%20access%20to%20a%20vast%20catalog%20of%20games%20without%20a%20console.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20high%20144Hz%20refresh%20rate%20with%20PCs.%20Both%20of%20those%20features%20were%20missing%20on%20last%20year's%20C4.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20C5%20levels%20the%20playing%20field.%20It%20now%20supports%20cloud%20gaming%20through%20the%20Xbox%20app%20and%20a%20144Hz%20refresh%20rate%20with%20PCs.%20It%20also%20uses%20Nvidia%20G-Sync%20and%20AMD%20FreeSync%20Premium%20variable%20refresh%20rate%20(VRR)%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20played%20%26quot%3BClair%20Obscur%3A%20Expedition%2033%26quot%3B%20through%20the%20Xbox%20app%20with%20a%20wired%20Gigabit%20connection%2C%20and%20overall%20was%20impressed.%20The%20image%20still%20isn't%20as%20detailed%20as%20it%20is%20when%20playing%20the%20game%20locally%20on%20my%20Xbox%20Series%20X%2C%20and%20streaming%20causes%20some%20posterization%20(likely%20from%20compression)%2C%20especially%20in%20dark%20portions%20of%20the%20screen%2C%20but%20the%20game%20was%20responsive.%20I%20would%20still%20opt%20for%20a%20console%20to%20get%20the%20best%20visuals%2C%20but%20using%20the%20app%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20get%20your%20gaming%20fix%20without%20dropping%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20for%20a%20Series%20S%20or%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20small%20drawback%20to%20using%20cloud%20gaming%20instead%20of%20a%20console%20is%20that%20LG's%20Game%20Optimizer%20menu%20is%20only%20available%20with%20an%20HDMI%20connection.%20I'm%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20Game%20Optimizer%20menu%2C%20which%20displays%20frame%20rate%2C%20VRR%2C%20latency%2C%20and%20black%20stabilizer%20information%20while%20making%20access%20to%20these%20gaming%20features%20quick%20and%20easy.%20Pressing%20the%20settings%20button%20on%20the%20remote%20will%20open%20the%20Game%20Optimizer%20menu%20instead%20of%20the%20usual%20settings%20menu%20you%20get%20while%20watching%20regular%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20issue%20with%20the%20default%20Game%20Optimizer%20Picture%20Mode%20is%20that%20its%20color%20leans%20very%20blue.%20This%20does%20make%20the%20image%20appear%20brighter%2C%20but%20it%20causes%20the%20colors%20to%20be%20inaccurate.%20To%20bring%20the%20color%20accuracy%20in%20line%20with%20Filmmaker%20Mode%2C%20under%20the%20Picture%20menu%2C%20you%20can%20go%20to%20Advanced%20Settings%2C%20then%20Color%2C%20White%20Balance%2C%20and%20change%20Color%20Temperature%20from%200%20to%20Warm%2040.%20I%20also%20switched%20Color%20Gamut%20from%20Native%20to%20Auto%20Detect%2C%20and%20boosted%20OLED%20Pixel%20Brightness%20in%20the%20Brightness%20menu%20up%20to%20100%20(from%20the%20default%20of%2080).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222dde2b71-8ad4-4f5c-9cea-2a0f040df592%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20and%20AI%20features%5C%22%3ENew%20AI%20features%20are%20mostly%20unnecessary%2C%20but%20Voice%20ID%20is%20a%20cool%20addition%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222651%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20of%20an%20LG%20C5%20OLED%20switching%20accounts%20on%20its%20homepage%20using%20Voice%20ID.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6830d0f1ca50259add4cf61e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221989%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20C5%20can%20recognize%20your%20voice%20and%20switch%20user%20profiles%20automatically.%3Cp%3ELG%2FBest%20Buy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20LG%20is%20touting%20a%20few%20new%20AI%20software%20features%20for%20its%20webOS%20smart%20TV%20system.%20A%20new%20AI%20Sound%20Wizard%20joins%20the%20previously%20available%20AI%20Picture%20Wizard.%20These%20modes%20let%20you%20customize%20your%20picture%20and%20sound%20settings%20by%20viewing%20different%20images%20and%20listening%20to%20different%20audio%20clips.%20Based%20on%20which%20images%20and%20audio%20clips%20you%20select%2C%20the%20system%20learns%20what%20kind%20of%20picture%20and%20sound%20elements%20you%20favor%20and%20then%20creates%20custom%20settings%20based%20on%20your%20preferences.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20sounds%20cool%20in%20theory%2C%20these%20modes%20generally%20introduce%20unnecessary%20adjustments.%20If%20you're%20unhappy%20with%20any%20of%20the%20TV's%20built-in%20presets%2C%20it%20could%20be%20worth%20giving%20the%20AI%20Wizards%20a%20whirl%2C%20but%20you%20can%20get%20the%20most%20accurate%20performance%20by%20simply%20choosing%20the%20TV's%20Filmmaker%20picture%20mode%20and%20Standard%20sound%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20more%20interesting%20addition%2C%20though%2C%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20have%20up%20to%2010%20different%20user%20profiles%20with%20unique%20preferences%20and%20content%20recommendations.%20Each%20profile%20can%20be%20tied%20to%20a%20Voice%20ID%20(after%20you%20agree%20to%20share%20your%20biometric%20data)%2C%20so%20the%20TV%20will%20automatically%20switch%20to%20your%20profile%20when%20you%20speak%20into%20the%20remote.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20it%20only%20took%20a%20few%20seconds%20for%20the%20profile%20switch%20to%20happen.%20The%20profile%20is%20linked%20to%20your%20LG%20account%2C%20and%20the%20settings%20and%20layout%20preferences%20are%20saved%20in%20the%20cloud%2C%20so%20you%20could%20sign%20into%20your%20friend's%20C5%20when%20you%20visit%20to%20pull%20up%20your%20own%20preferences%20easily%20(as%20long%20as%20there's%20space%20to%20add%20your%20account).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20niche%20example%2C%20but%20the%20ability%20for%20a%20family%20to%20easily%20switch%20between%20profiles%20so%20kids%20can%20access%20the%20apps%20most%20interesting%20to%20them%2C%20while%20one%20of%20their%20parents%20can%20later%20speak%20into%20the%20remote%20and%20call%20up%20their%20profile%20setup%20is%20an%20intriguing%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20LG's%20webOS%20smart%20TV%20system%20remains%20much%20the%20same%20as%20it%20was%20last%20year.%20That%20is%20to%20say%2C%20it%20gets%20the%20job%20done%20but%20isn't%20likely%20to%20wow%20you.%20You%20get%20access%20to%20all%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20streaming%20apps%2C%20and%20navigation%20speed%20is%20solid.%20The%20interface's%20emphasis%20on%20ads%20and%20shopping%20recommendations%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20drag%2C%20but%20you%20can%20disable%20these%20from%20appearing%20through%20the%20menu%20system.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f15e9a4-2053-4ee0-b392-c881ccd803ff%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Wireless%20sound%5C%22%3EWhile%20sound%20performance%20is%20lacking%2C%20Auracast%20inclusion%20is%20a%20welcome%20perk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221147%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20lifestyle%20image%20of%20an%20LG%20C5%20OLED%20hanging%20on%20a%20wall%20with%20a%20soundbar%20mounted%20underneath%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6830d27fca50259add4cf68c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22860%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20recommend%20you%20pair%20the%20C5%20with%20a%20soundbar%20or%20surround%20sound%20system%20to%20get%20the%20best%20audio%20performance.%3Cp%3ELG%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20few%20TVs%20out%20there%20with%20sound%20I%20would%20call%20decent.%20It's%20an%20inherent%20flaw%20due%20to%20the%20thin%20design%20of%20modern%20displays%2C%20and%20very%20few%20are%20able%20to%20overcome%20it.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20C5%20falls%20victim%20to%20this%20common%20pitfall.%20While%20dialogue%20can%20generally%20be%20heard%20clearly%2C%20the%20sound%20is%20thin%20and%20a%20bit%20tinny.%20If%20you're%20buying%20a%20set%20like%20this%2C%20it's%20worth%20adding%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-soundbars%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoundbar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20package%20to%20enhance%20the%20overall%20performance.%20Or%20better%20yet%2C%20an%20AVR%20with%20a%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-surround-sound-systems%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esurround%20sound%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20note%2C%20the%20C5%20does%20have%20an%20interesting%20feature%20that%20I%20hope%20to%20see%20added%20to%20more%20TVs%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bluetooth.com%2Fauracast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAuracast%3C%2Fa%3E%20support.%20Samsung%20started%20to%20support%20it%20with%20select%20models%20in%202023%2C%20but%20it's%20nice%20to%20see%20it%20on%20the%20C5.%20Auracast%20allows%20the%20TV%20to%20transmit%20over%20Bluetooth%20to%20any%20number%20of%20devices%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20being%20limited%20to%20a%20single%20device.%20I%20tested%20this%20with%20a%20few%20different%20Auracast-capable%20headphones%20and%20earbuds%2C%20including%20the%20JBL%20Tour%20One%20M3%20headphones%2C%20Earfun%20Air%20Pro%204%20earbuds%2C%20and%20the%20LG%20xboom%20Buds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Sound%20menu%2C%20you%20can%20turn%20on%20Auracast%20broadcasting%20and%20select%20a%20quality%20level%3A%2016kHz%2C%2024kHz%2C%20or%2048kHz.%20Then%2C%20from%20your%20headphones%20app%2C%20you%20can%20connect%20to%20the%20broadcast%20signal%20with%20any%20number%20of%20devices.%20With%20the%20JBL%20and%20the%20LG%20headphones%2C%20the%20process%20worked%20flawlessly%20with%20audio%20playing%20through%20both%2C%20and%20I%20could%20watch%20without%20distracting%20my%20family%20or%20worrying%20about%20being%20too%20loud%20for%20my%20neighbors%20late%20at%20night.%20The%20Earfun%20were%20a%20bit%20tricky%20to%20get%20to%20work%2C%20but%20that%20was%20a%20fault%20of%20the%20earbuds%20and%20their%20app%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20C5.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20no%20lag%20between%20headphones%20and%20the%20TV%2C%20so%20the%20Auracast%20connection%20could%20help%20people%20better%20control%20t