%20we%20break%20the%20news%20to%20people%3F%20Should%20we%20start%20getting%20the%20nursery%20ready%3F%20Should%20we%20buy%20things%20for%20the%20baby%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20decision%20was%20a%20conundrum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20Radhika%20lean%20into%20the%20side%20of%20hope%20or%20not%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20figured%2C%20hope%20is%20a%20capricious%20dynamic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20every%20day%20was%20the%20same.%20You%20can%20only%20hold%20on%20to%20hope%20and%20faith%2C%20and%20believe%20that%20things%20will%20be%20okay%2C%20but%20there%20are%20moments%20when%20you%20doubt%20it.%20There%20was%20major%20coexistence%20of%20joy%20and%20fear%20in%20my%20life%20at%20that%20point%2C%20because%20we%20never%20knew%20what%20the%20next%20stage%20would%20hold.%20At%20every%20stage%2C%20there%20were%20so%20many%20fears%20we%20dealt%20with.%20We%20would%20often%20wonder%20whether%20the%20next%20ultrasound%20would%20be%20fine%20or%20reveal%20something.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhika%E2%80%99s%20fear%20was%20realised%20when%2C%20after%20one%20particular%2020-week%20ultrasound%2C%20the%20doctor%20informed%20her%20that%20the%20foetus%20had%20a%20short%20nasal%20bone%2C%20which%20could%20be%20suggestive%20of%20Down%E2%80%99s%20Syndrome.%20%E2%80%9CShould%20the%20test%20come%20positive%2C%20I%20was%20recommended%20not%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20pregnancy.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20was%20negative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnxiety%20revisited%20her%20once%20more%20when%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20gestational%20diabetes.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20levels%20were%20impossible.%20So%20from%20a%20person%20who%20feared%20needles%2C%20I%20became%20someone%20who%20would%20prick%20myself%20multiple%20times%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%2