.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENature-integrated%20infrastructure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Strategically%20designed%20urban%20green%20spaces%E2%80%94including%20tree%20canopies%2C%20bioswales%2C%20and%20buffer%20zones%E2%80%94play%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20reducing%20particulate%20matter%2C%20regulating%20microclimates%2C%20and%20enhancing%20ecological%20resilience.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EESG%20integration%20for%20MSMEs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Embedding%20Environmental%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Governance%20(ESG)%20frameworks%20within%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20is%20key%20to%20diffusing%20sustainable%20practices%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20industrial%20base%2C%20which%20is%20often%20overlooked%20in%20regulatory%20discourse.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuman-centred%20urban%20design%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Cities%20must%20be%20envisioned%20around%20the%20needs%20of%20their%20most%20vulnerable%20residents%E2%80%94children%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20low-income%20communities.%20This%20entails%20the%20development%20of%20inclusive%20mobility%20corridors%2C%20accessible%20public%20spaces%2C%20and%20transit%20ecosystems%20that%20prioritise%20safety%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20environmental%20integrity.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20tech%20meets%20trees%3A%20The%20future%20is%20hybrid%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20World%20Environment%20Expo%2C%20I%20examined%20the%20intersection%20of%20emerging%20technologies%20and%20nature-based%20solutions%20(NBS)%2C%20highlighting%20the%20potential%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20the%20Internet%20of%20Things%20(IoT)%2C%20and%20blockchain%20to%20enhance%20urban%20ecological%20resilience.%20These%20technologies%20can%20enable%20predictive%20analytics%20for%20pollution%20patterns%2C%20optimise%20irrigation%20for%20urban%20green%20infrastructure%20based%20on%20real-time%20meteorological%20data%2C%20and%20ensure%20transparency%20in%20envi